data.description: Incredible opportunity and price on this luxury Home with casual elegance in the gated community of Hidden Valley Lake! Spacious 3,077 square feet with 4 large bedrooms and 3 baths also an office/den/family room that could be a fifth bedroom. Gorgeous granite kitchen with all the extras including newer Whirlpool Gold Series appliances, and hardwood floors that carry through the formal dining and entry. The living room has soaring ceilings and a gas fireplace. The living room and Bonus rooms are wired for surround sound. Bathrooms are tastefully tiled and appointed. An extra-large laundry suite has plenty of storage and features a color-designated water manifold system. The primary suite is on the main level, downstairs has a wide gentle stairway leading to 3 more bedrooms a large bath, and a family room. Dual-Zoned HVAC and a Generac whole house generator is included. The backyard is fully fenced and a storage shed will come in handy. Solar leased, keeps the cost down and will be assumed by the buyer. All of this is found at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac close to the lake.
